Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45}Amber Volt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然大白天公会里都没人上线呢
